---
import '../styles/index.css';
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout 
    title="Fitur Lengkap Aplikasi Kasir Pintar Jaripos | AI-powered POS"
    description="Pelajari fitur canggih Jaripos: Rekomendasi Stok AI, Jari AI Chatbot, cetak struk Bluetooth, kelola multi-kasir, dan laporan laba-rugi otomatis untuk UMKM."
    keywords="fitur kasir, aplikasi kasir pintar, AI inventory, rekomendasi stok, chatbot bisnis, pos bluetooth, multi outlet, laporan laba rugi"
>
    <Navbar />

    <main class="relative z-10 bg-white text-slate-600 pt-32">
        <!-- Hero & Header Wrapper with Light Geometric Mesh -->
        <div class="hero-light-wrapper border-b border-slate-100">
            <div class="mesh-grid-light"></div>
            <!-- Hero Section -->
            <section class="py-20 relative overflow-hidden">
                <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10 text-center">
                    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black tracking-tight text-[#121417] mb-6">
                        Teknologi Kasir Pintar <br/>
                        <span class="text-[#1f5aa2]">Di Ujung Jari Anda</span>
                    </h1>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg md:text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-10 leading-relaxed">
                        Lebih dari sekadar mencatat penjualan. Jaripos menggabungkan otomatisasi praktis dengan antarmuka yang sangat ringkas untuk mendongkrak keuntungan usaha Anda.
                    </p>
                    <div class="flex justify-center gap-4">
                        <a href="https://app.jaripos.com/register" class="group inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full px-8 py-4 font-bold text-white bg-[#1f5aa2] hover:bg-[#164075] active:scale-95 transition-colors duration-300 ease-out shadow-lg shadow-[#1f5aa2]/20 gap-2">
                            <span>Coba Gratis Sekarang</span>
                            <svg class="h-5 w-5 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path></svg>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>

        <!-- Core Features (Alternating Layouts) -->
        <section class="py-20 bg-slate-50 border-t border-slate-100">
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 space-y-32">
                
                <!-- Feature 1 -->
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center">
                    <div class="lg:col-span-6 space-y-6" data-aos="fade-right">
                        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 tracking-tight">
                            Asisten Bisnis Praktis: <br/>
                            <span class="text-[#1f5aa2]">Laporan & Analisis Penjualan</span>
                        </h2>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                            Punya pertanyaan tentang performa toko? Tidak perlu bongkar ribuan baris excel. Dapatkan ringkasan otomatis harian dan bulanan secara praktis.
                        </p>
                        <ul class="space-y-3">
                            <li class="flex items-center gap-2.5 text-sm text-slate-600 font-medium">
                                <span class="text-[#1f5aa2]">✓</span> Pantau performa harian ("Ringkasan omzet hari ini dibanding kemarin")
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-center gap-2.5 text-sm text-slate-600 font-medium">
                                <span class="text-[#1f5aa2]">✓</span> Analisis tren penjualan ("Waktu tersibuk transaksi toko Anda")
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-center gap-2.5 text-sm text-slate-600 font-medium">
                                <span class="text-[#1f5aa2]">✓</span> Proyeksi keuntungan bersih dengan data terintegrasi.
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="lg:col-span-6" data-aos="fade-left">
                        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 shadow-xl relative overflow-hidden">
                            <!-- Mockup Chat -->
                            <div class="space-y-4 font-mono text-xs">
                                <div class="bg-slate-100 p-4 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 max-w-[85%] self-end ml-auto">
                                    <p class="text-slate-500 mb-1 font-sans">Anda</p>
                                    <p class="text-slate-800 font-sans">Barang apa yang paling laris minggu ini dan bagaimana stoknya?</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="bg-[#1f5aa2]/5 p-4 rounded-2xl border border-[#1f5aa2]/20 max-w-[85%]">
                                    <p class="text-[#1f5aa2] mb-1 font-sans font-bold">📊 Jaripos Assistant</p>
                                    <p class="text-slate-700 font-sans leading-relaxed">
                                        Produk terlaris adalah <strong>Kopi Susu Gula Aren</strong> (terjual 142 cup). Stok bahan baku Espresso saat ini tersisa untuk 30 porsi. Direkomendasikan melakukan re-stock kopi arabika sebelum hari Jumat.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Feature 2 -->
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center lg:flex-row-reverse">
                    <div class="lg:col-span-6 lg:order-2 space-y-6" data-aos="fade-left">
                        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 tracking-tight">
                            Prediksi Stok Cerdas: <br/>
                            <span class="text-[#1f5aa2]">Manajemen & Restock Otomatis</span>
                        </h2>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                            Jangan biarkan stok habis saat pelanggan datang atau modal mati karena stok menumpuk terlalu banyak. Sistem menganalisis kecepatan jualan dan memberikan estimasi waktu restock yang tepat.
                        </p>
                        <ul class="space-y-3">
                            <li class="flex items-center gap-2.5 text-sm text-slate-600 font-medium">
                                <span class="text-[#1f5aa2]">✓</span> Notifikasi otomatis saat stok mendekati batas minimum.
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-center gap-2.5 text-sm text-slate-600 font-medium">
                                <span class="text-[#1f5aa2]">✓</span> Analisis barang macet untuk menghindari kerugian modal.
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-center gap-2.5 text-sm text-slate-600 font-medium">
                                <span class="text-[#1f5aa2]">✓</span> Rekomendasi jumlah pembelian barang ke supplier.
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="lg:col-span-6 lg:order-1" data-aos="fade-right">
                        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 shadow-xl relative overflow-hidden">
                            <!-- Stock Alert Mockup -->
                            <div class="space-y-3 font-sans text-xs">
                                <div class="bg-slate-50 p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-between">
                                    <div>
                                        <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-sm">Susu UHT Full Cream</h4>
                                        <p class="text-slate-500 mt-1">Sisa 5 Pcs (Batas Minimum: 10)</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <span class="px-2.5 py-1 bg-rose-50 border border-rose-200 text-rose-600 rounded-md font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-[10px]">Stok Kritis</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="bg-slate-50 p-4 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 flex items-center justify-between">
                                    <div>
                                        <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-sm">Gula Pasir 1kg</h4>
                                        <p class="text-slate-500 mt-1">Sisa 35 Pcs (Habis dalam ~4 hari)</p>
                                    </div>
                                    <span class="px-2.5 py-1 bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 text-amber-600 rounded-md font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-[10px]">Perlu Restock</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Standard POS Features Grid -->
        <section class="py-24 bg-white relative overflow-hidden border-t border-slate-100">
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
                <div class="text-center mb-20" data-aos="fade-up">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black text-slate-900">Seluruh Kebutuhan Kasir Terpenuhi</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-500 mt-4 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Kami menyediakan fitur standar industri retail & F&B dengan optimalisasi kecepatan operasional.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                    <!-- Fitur 1: Bluetooth -->
                    <div class="p-8 bg-white rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-[#1f5aa2]/40 transition-all duration-300 group">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-[#1f5aa2]/10 flex items-center justify-center text-[#1f5aa2] mb-6 font-bold text-lg">
                            <i class="fas fa-[#1f5aa2] fa-print"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-display text-slate-900 mb-3">Cetak Struk Bluetooth</h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Hubungkan HP Anda dengan printer thermal ukuran 58mm atau 80mm via bluetooth secara mulus. Tanpa driver yang rumit.</p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Fitur 2: Multi-Kasir -->
                    <div class="p-8 bg-white rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-[#1f5aa2]/40 transition-all duration-300 group">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-[#1f5aa2]/10 flex items-center justify-center text-[#1f5aa2] mb-6 font-bold text-lg">
                            <i class="fas fa-[#1f5aa2] fa-users-gear"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-display text-slate-900 mb-3">Multi-Kasir & Role Akses</h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Tambah staf kasir sebanyak yang Anda butuhkan. Batasi hak akses mereka (kasir, admin, owner) untuk menjaga kerahasiaan keuangan toko.</p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Fitur 3: Laporan Keuangan -->
                    <div class="p-8 bg-white rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-[#1f5aa2]/40 transition-all duration-300 group">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-[#1f5aa2]/10 flex items-center justify-center text-[#1f5aa2] mb-6 font-bold text-lg">
                            <i class="fas fa-[#1f5aa2] fa-chart-pie"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-display text-slate-900 mb-3">Laporan Laba/Rugi Real-Time</h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Pantau grafik omzet, laba kotor, laba bersih, barang paling menguntungkan, hingga performa kasir secara real-time dari mana saja.</p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Fitur 4: Pembayaran Digital -->
                    <div class="p-8 bg-white rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-[#1f5aa2]/40 transition-all duration-300 group">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-[#1f5aa2]/10 flex items-center justify-center text-[#1f5aa2] mb-6 font-bold text-lg">
                            <i class="fas fa-[#1f5aa2] fa-credit-card"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-display text-slate-900 mb-3">QRIS & Metode Pembayaran</h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Menerima pembayaran tunai, debit, kartu kredit, hingga e-wallet. Cetak struk dengan QRIS dinamis untuk kemudahan pembayaran nontunai.</p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Fitur 5: Aplikasi PWA Ringan -->
                    <div class="p-8 bg-white rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-[#1f5aa2]/40 transition-all duration-300 group">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-[#1f5aa2]/10 flex items-center justify-center text-[#1f5aa2] mb-6 font-bold text-lg">
                            <i class="fas fa-[#1f5aa2] fa-mobile-screen-button"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-display text-slate-900 mb-3">Aplikasi Ringan & Offline Mode</h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Teknologi PWA membuat Jaripos bisa dijalankan langsung dari browser HP Anda layaknya aplikasi native tanpa memakan memori penyimpanan.</p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Fitur 6: Manajemen Pelanggan -->
                    <div class="p-8 bg-white rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-[#1f5aa2]/40 transition-all duration-300 group">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-[#1f5aa2]/10 flex items-center justify-center text-[#1f5aa2] mb-6 font-bold text-lg">
                            <i class="fas fa-[#1f5aa2] fa-tags"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-display text-slate-900 mb-3">Promo & Diskon Fleksibel</h3>
                        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Buat skema diskon persentase, nominal, atau beli-X-gratis-Y. Naikkan retensi pelanggan dengan manajemen membership sederhana.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Final CTA -->
        <section class="py-24 bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-50 to-white border-t border-slate-100 text-center relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-6">Nikmati Kemudahan Mengelola Bisnis</h2>
                <p class="text-slate-600 text-md md:text-lg mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                    Daftar sekarang dan nikmati seluruh fitur di atas secara gratis selama 14 hari penuh. Tanpa komitmen kartu kredit.
                </p>
                <div class="flex justify-center gap-4 flex-wrap">
                    <a href="https://app.jaripos.com/register" class="group inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full px-8 py-4 font-bold text-white bg-[#1f5aa2] hover:bg-[#164075] active:scale-95 transition-colors duration-300 ease-out shadow-lg shadow-[#1f5aa2]/20 gap-2">
                        <span>Mulai Trial 14 Hari</span>
                        <svg class="h-5 w-5 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path></svg>
                    </a>
                    <a href="/harga" class="px-8 py-4 bg-white border-2 border-slate-200 hover:bg-slate-50 hover:border-slate-300 active:scale-95 transition-colors duration-300 ease-out font-semibold text-slate-700 rounded-full inline-flex items-center justify-center">
                        Lihat Daftar Harga
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <Footer />
</Layout>
